{"tid":1611972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要屌你哋對黨鐵狗窿完全冇危機意識！入嚟！","createTime":"2019-10-02T06:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:10:42.000Z","uid":265252,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9e50baa97a3d3dbf48d5ec1bd1bb4824307b63ce","tid":1611972,"uid":265252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXudBdo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXudBdo.png&h=3f675cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGJRnTq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGJRnTq.png&h=9a4f44b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9.29嘅教訓，大家應該歷歷在目。<br />\n速龍喺政總兩隻暗門同埋金鐘地鐵站突擊出嚟拉咗接近一百個，全部今日提堂！<br />\n<br />\n依家黨鐵做咗最大嘅流動狗中心，喺金鐘中環呢啲滿佈黨鐵地面出口嘅版圖，大家尋日仍然係冇封黨鐵狗窿嘅意識，搬兩個垃圾桶喺鐵閘口就以為啲畜狗出唔到嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真係屌晒你哋係咪想死呀？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果你哋想呢場運動可以繼續，唔撚該、麻撚煩你哋以後每人行多步，做好防禦工事！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>除咗花生油植物油橄欖油令到個地下好Hi跣，膨脹膠封咗個鎖係好撚麻煩之外，如果係兩邊拉埋嘅閘，尋日黃大仙手足就做咗個完美示範，記住咁樣係會救翻好多人！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/D8PaUIumgJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD8PaUIumgJM&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=6832579c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/D8PaUIumgJM</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n地面推進嘅防暴狗每次都跑唔到超過60米架！如果可以令死畜龍冇咗奇襲效果，被捕人數會大大大大撚幅減少！<br />\n<br />\n記住鐵線、單車鏈同油、缺一不可！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1862089218ff3daf238bab7c4e1a03c7e35caa08","tid":1611972,"uid":265252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"唔該推下"},{"pid":"47b591760ca508359746cdb27685e6fd7403c6f4","tid":1611972,"uid":267937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f88267d14610f9081d57a312623d3479696a75d6","tid":1611972,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:10:10.000Z","msg":"黨鐵咁撚鍾意封站<br />\n一於幫佢封實啲"},{"pid":"097ad6f4b027e054308a66fb3c8f6207b407d0b1","tid":1611972,"uid":63464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"推，全人類帶鐵線、單車鏈同油"},{"pid":"1ddea5ace3707df1cfe1ba88bcd4a174a19ed2d4","tid":1611972,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"尋日有手足倒柔順劑，有無用？<br />\n使唔使加少少水，混合左先倒？"},{"pid":"c2fd549cc00d175d961511eaa45bb1e657d11e03","tid":1611972,"uid":265252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:14:13.000Z","msg":"柔順劑洗潔精花生油橄欖油咩都好"},{"pid":"0a5cde9e06f9ff2a4f0611dc7715151d18d15022","tid":1611972,"uid":210016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c30f4177ea84eeb40f5a85512d54d14bd70925ee","tid":1611972,"uid":173850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:23:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e934268a4d99e30e491064ed9282feb5457a7e7b","tid":1611972,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"條片班畜生成堆傻閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77f83382b61013b7ed610dd970ff4c5a772aa83","tid":1611972,"uid":106580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:45:27.000Z","msg":"721 811 831 101<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e930d8126707a0ab0da1bb00e9e0bdf20555c94","tid":1611972,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"等佢解鎖時施放魔法<br />\nBBQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}